    "# GamePulse — 02 · Silver Layer\n",
    "## Data Cleaning & Standardization\n",
    "\n",
    "**SYST52461 – Big Data Storage and Analysis**  \n",
    "**Term Project · Winter 2026**\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "### Purpose\n",
    "This notebook reads the four Bronze tables, applies data quality fixes, and writes clean **Silver** Delta tables.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Cleaning Applied\n",
    "| Table | Issues Fixed |\n",
    "|---|---|\n",
    "| `players` | Standardize `region` + `account_type` to title case; cast `age` to integer; cast `join_date` to date; drop null `email` rows |\n",
    "| `games` | Standardize `genre` + `game_mode` to title case; drop null `game_mode` rows |\n",
    "| `game_sessions` | Cast `session_date` to date; drop rows with `duration_minutes` ≤ 0; impute null `score` with 0 |\n",
    "| `purchases` | Standardize `category` to title case; cast `purchase_date` to date; drop rows with `amount_spent` ≤ 0 |"
   ]
