    "## Silver Layer Data Cleaning Strategy\n",
    "\n",
    "This layer focuses on transforming raw Bronze data into clean, standardized datasets.\n",
    "\n",
    "Key steps include:\n",
    "- Handling missing values (dropping or imputing where appropriate)\n",
    "- Standardizing categorical fields such as region and account_type\n",
    "- Converting data types (e.g., string → integer, string → date)\n",
    "- Removing invalid records (e.g., negative spending, zero-duration sessions)\n",
    "\n",
    "These transformations ensure data consistency and prepare it for reliable aggregation in the Gold layer."
   ]
